                                <ol start="1">
                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">To administer and improve our Website and for internal operations, including troubleshooting, data analysis, testing, research, statistical and survey purposes.</span></li>
                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">As part of our efforts to keep our Website safe and secure.</span></li>
                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">To measure or understand the effectiveness of advertising we serve to you and others, and to deliver relevant advertising to you.</span></li>
                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">To make suggestions and recommendations to you and other users of our Website about services that may interest you or them;</span></li>
