                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">To fulfill our obligations arising from our contract with you, and to allow you to fulfil your contractual obligation to us, such as by accessing the Services as a Writer or Content Provider (as defined in our Terms of Service for Writers);</span></li>
                                    <li class="atlas-block atlas-block-list-item"><span class="atlas-leaf">To liaise with you about projects that you are undertaking for us.</span></li>
